cast.overview: Pakistan-born comedian Kumail Nanjiani and grad student Emily Gardner fall in love but struggle as their cultures clash. When Emily contracts a mysterious illness, Kumail finds himself forced to face her feisty parents, his family's expectations, and his true feelings.
cast.title: The Big Sick

details.biography: Jack Corrigan is an American film and television child actor, has been acting/modeling since he was born! He has also been playing tackle football since 1st grade!  He has been featured in many short films, TV, Commercials, Webseries, Live performances and  & Much more!  Jack could not be more excited to combine his lover for Football & Acting in this role in the short film "Running Scared".
details.name: Jack Corrigan
